<h3>Logistics Charges</h3>
<span style="font-weight: 400;">These charges are applicable only toÂ LMD sellers. TheÂ charges are calculated by taking the higher of volumetric weight and the original weight of the shipment. Â The volumetric weight is calculated by simply dividing the volume (in cubic cm) by a factor of 5 which is then compared with the actual weight in grams. Â This weight is then multiplied by the logistics rate asÂ explained below.</span>
<h3>Charges</h3>
<ul>
	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">For BD surface, it will be 20/- for every 1kg, where minimum charge is Rs.140 for initial 7kg</span></li>
</ul>
<span style="font-weight: 400;">For example:</span>
<table style="height: 146px;" width="185">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td width="67">WEIGHT</td>
<td width="68">CHARGES</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>4 KG</td>
<td>RS. 140</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>7 KG</td>
<td style="text-align: left;">RS. 140</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>10 KG</td>
<td>RS. 200</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
For other shippers:

<span style="font-weight: 400;">Logistic will be Rs. 45/- for every 500 gm, where Rs.50 will be charged for the first 500 gm.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">
</span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">For example</span>
<table style="height: 141px;" width="180">
