</tr>
<tr>
<td>1.5 KG</td>
<td>RS. 140</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<b>NOTE:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">Â These charges are exclusive of taxes.</span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">Final Logistics is deducted on weight of fulfillments created and then amount is equally divided on each item based on weight of individual item.</span>

